eclasstool.model.roster

Class RosterModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • eclasstool.model.roster.RosterModel

  • public class RosterModel
extends java.util.Observable
    Class Roster is the model class for the main EClass Roster UI handling. It contains methods for mananging the classroom's attendee. The data component of the roster is a collecton of student objects. There are two operations involved - clicking on a student's question bubble if it arises, and another to assign a privilege on the roster. Students are imported from an external source. Assume Collection of students are filled.
